# OpenCDS pinned commits — "Digital Tablet" build pin for the Breath-Ezy CDS gateway.
#
# These are the EXACT commit hashes of the 7 OpenCDS repositories that produced a
# working build + deploy on 2026-07-14 (OpenCDS 7.1.0-SNAPSHOT, Java 17, Tomcat 11).
# Pinning them makes the gateway image reproducible, per the breath-ezy charter
# <standards_pins> discipline ("do not silently bump"). OpenCDS uses SNAPSHOT-only
# versioning with no tagged releases, so an exact SHA is the only stable pin.
#
# Source: bitbucket.org/opencds/<repo>. Bump only under an approved plan.

